definition.value: Modulates the rate of GTP hydrolysis by a GTPase.
Catalysis of the transfer of a methyl group from a donor to the C5 atom of the uridine residue at position 54 in a tRNA molecule.

Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + tRNA -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + tRNA containing thymine at position U54 of a transfer RNA. This occurs in most Gram-negative bacteria, some archae, and eukaryotes.

Catalysis of the transfer of a methyl group from 5,10-methylenetetrahydrofolate to the C5 atom of the uridine residue at position 54 in a tRNA molecule. This occurs in most Gram-positive bacteria and some Gram-negative bacteria.
Catalysis of the reaction -  acetyl phosphate + H(2)O + NH(4)(+) + thioredoxin disulfide -eq- glycine + H(+) + phosphate + thioredoxin.

Complex that possesses glycine reductase activity -  usually comprises three subunits, of which two are selenoproteins -  the subunits are typically designated selenoprotein A, selenoprotein B and protein C.
Catalysis of the reaction -  NAD+ + [dinitrogen reductase] -eq- nicotinamide + ADP-D-ribosyl-[dinitrogen reductase].
Repression of transcription of centromeric DNA by altering the structure of chromatin.
Catalysis of the reaction -  acetoacetate + ATP + CoA -eq- acetoacetyl-CoA + AMP + diphosphate + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + guanidinoacetate -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + creatine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + L-methionine -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + S-methyl-L-methionine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + a fatty acid -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + a fatty acid methyl ester.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + 1,4-N1-D-glucooligosaccharide -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + oligosaccharide containing 6-methyl-D-glucose units.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + carnosine -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + anserine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + phenol -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + anisole + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-iodophenol + S-adenosyl-L-methionine -eq- 1-iodo-2-methoxybenzene + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + tyramine -eq- N-methyltyramine + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + O-demethylpuromycin -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + puromycin.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) + myo-inositol -eq- 1D-3-O-methyl-myo-inositol + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) + myo-inositol -eq- 1D-1-O-methyl-myo-inositol + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Interacting selectively and non-covalently with any protein or protein complex (a complex of two or more proteins that may include other nonprotein molecules) using energy from the hydrolysis of GTP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + rRNA -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + rRNA containing a single residue of 2'-O-methyladenosine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + luteolin -eq- 4',5,7-trihydroxy-3'-methoxyflavone + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + N-alpha,N-alpha-dimethyl-L-histidine -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + N-alpha,N-alpha,N-alpha-trimethyl-L-histidine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + isoflavone -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + 4'-O-methylisoflavone.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + (indol-3-yl)pyruvate -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + (S)-3-(indol-3-yl)-2-oxobutanoate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + an amine -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + a methylated amine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + loganate -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + loganin.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + putrescine -eq- N-methylputrescine + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) + licodione -eq- 2'-O-methyllicodione + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + 5-hydroxyfuranocoumarin -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + 5-methoxyfuranocoumarin.

Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + xanthotoxol -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + xanthotoxin. Xanthotoxol is also known as 8-hydroxyfuranocoumarin and xanthotoxin as 8-methoxyfuranocoumarin.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + 5,7,4'-trihydroxyflavone -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + 4'-methoxy-5,7-dihydroxyflavone.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + 3,5,7,3',4'-pentahydroxyflavone -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + 3-methoxy-5,7,3',4'-tetrahydroxy-flavone.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) + isoorientin -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+) + isoscoparin.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3',4',5,7-tetrahydroxy-3-methoxyflavone + S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) -eq- 3',4',5-trihydroxy-3,7-dimethoxyflavone + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3',4',5-trihydroxy-3,7-dimethoxyflavone + S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) -eq- 3',5-dihydroxy-3,4',7-trimethoxyflavone + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  3',4',5,6-tetrahydroxy-3,7-dimethoxyflavone + S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) -eq- 3',4',5-trihydroxy-3,6,7-trimethoxyflavone + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) + pyridine -eq- N-methylpyridinium + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3,3',4',5,7,8-hexahydroxyflavone + S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) -eq- 3,3',4',5,7-pentahydroxy-8-methoxyflavone + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  (S)-tetrahydrocolumbamine + S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+) + tetrahydropalmatine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-methylpropanal oxime + S-adenosyl-L-methionine -eq- 2-methylpropanal O-methyloxime + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + 11-O-demethyl-17-O-deacetylvindoline -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + 17-O-deacetylvindoline.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3-hydroxyanthranilate + S-adenosyl-L-methionine -eq- 3-hydroxy-4-methylanthranilate + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  (3R)-3-hydroxy-16-methoxy-2,3-dihydrotabersonine + S-adenosyl-L-methionine -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + deacetoxyvindoline + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) + macrocin -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+) + tylosin.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) + demethylmacrocin -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+) + macrocin.
Catalysis of the reaction -  N-benzoyl-4-hydroxyanthranilate + S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) -eq- N-benzoyl-4-methoxyanthranilate + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine(1+) + L-tryptophan -eq- S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + L-2-methyltryptophan + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  6-hydroxymellein + S-adenosyl-L-methionine -eq- 6-methoxymellein + S-adenosyl-L-homocysteine + H(+).
